---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Our Methodology"
	description="Institutional-grade real estate analytics powered by AI."
	pubDate={new Date('May 16 2026')}
>
	<div class="about-content">
		<p class="lead">
			<strong>EstateIntel</strong> is a specialized platform dedicated to providing institutional-quality real estate insights. We bridge the gap between complex market data and actionable investment strategies.
		</p>

		<h2>Institutional Grade Analysis</h2>
		<p>
			Our methodology combines rigorous traditional financial analysis with advanced artificial intelligence. We process thousands of daily data points from official government sources (MOLIT) and news outlets to provide a comprehensive view of the market.
		</p>

		<div class="agent-system">
			<h3>The AI Agent Pipeline</h3>
			<div class="agent-grid">
				<div class="agent-card">
					<span class="agent-icon">🔍</span>
					<h4>Researcher</h4>
					<p>Aggregates global and local policy trends and news cycles.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="agent-card">
					<span class="agent-icon">📊</span>
					<h4>Analyst</h4>
					<p>Extracts precise transaction data and calculates moving averages.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="agent-card">
					<span class="agent-icon">🖋️</span>
					<h4>Writer</h4>
					<p>Synthesizes insights into structured, professional reports.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="agent-card">
					<span class="agent-icon">✨</span>
					<h4>Editor</h4>
					<p>Ensures consistent tone and clarity across all publications.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<h2>Precision and Objectivity</h2>
		<p>
			Real estate markets are often driven by sentiment. We prioritize <strong>data-driven objectivity</strong>, using 7-day moving averages and outlier filtering to provide a stable, reliable perspective on price movements and regional liquidity.
		</p>

		<p class="cta-text">
			Whether you are a professional investor or a homeowner, our goal is to provide the intelligence you need to navigate the evolving real estate landscape.
		</p>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about-content {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.lead {
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--primary);
		margin-bottom: 48px;
	}
	.agent-system {
		background: var(--primary);
		color: white;
		padding: 48px;
		border-radius: var(--rounded-lg);
		margin: 64px 0;
	}
	.agent-system h3 {
		color: white;
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: 32px;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.agent-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 24px;
	}
	.agent-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		padding: 24px;
		border-radius: var(--rounded-md);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}
	.agent-card h4 {
		color: var(--secondary-container);
		margin: 12px 0 8px;
	}
	.agent-card p {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		margin: 0;
	}
	.agent-icon {
		font-size: 24px;
	}
	.cta-text {
		font-style: italic;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
		padding-left: 24px;
		margin-top: 48px;
	}
	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.agent-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.agent-system { padding: 24px; }
	}
</style>
